{"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemecontrolitemcomponenttokensprovider"]}],"abstract":[{"text":"A class which wraps all ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"component  tokens","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":" for components with a ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"control item","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" layout like ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSSwitch","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSRadioButton","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" and ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSCheckboItem","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Contains also references to semantic tokens providers so as to be able to use them to define the component tokens.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"This provider should be integrated as a ","type":"text"},{"code":"AllControlItemComponentTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" implementation inside ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" so as to provide","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"all tokens to the users. It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" implementation to use.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Custom themes can use subclass of ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeControlItemComponentTokensProvider","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" and apply the provider they need.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"It implements also the protocol ","type":"text"},{"code":"ControlItemComponentTokens","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" so as to expose the component tokens for control-item-layout-basded components through any ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Such components tokens are defined with raw and semantic tokens of sizes (from ","type":"text"},{"code":"SizeSemanticTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":"),","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"borders (from ","type":"text"},{"code":"AllBorderSemanticTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":"),  colors (from ","type":"text"},{"code":"AllColorSemanticTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":")  and spaces (from ","type":"text"},{"code":"AllSpaceSemanticTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":").","type":"text"}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeControlItemComponentTokensProvider"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange"]]},"relationshipsSections":[{"kind":"relationships","type":"conformsTo","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/AllControlItemComponentTokensProvider","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/19OUDSTokensComponent011ControlItemB6TokensP","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/s8CopyableP","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/TokensProvider"],"title":"Conforms To"}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"metadata":{"externalID":"s:16OUDSThemesOrange0B39ThemeControlItemComponentTokensProviderC","symbolKind":"class","title":"OrangeThemeControlItemComponentTokensProvider","role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OrangeThemeControlItemComponentTokensProvider","kind":"identifier"}],"modules":[{"name":"Theme Orange"}],"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeControlItemComponentTokensProvider"}],"roleHeading":"Class"},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeControlItemComponentTokensProvider"}],"platforms":